  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u00a0\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Cancel the license of private buses that get diesel and sell it at higher prices - Bandula",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena has advised the authorities to immediately cancel the permit of private buses that are selling fuel at high prices without engaging in transport services by getting diesel from depots owned by the Transport Board.",
        "The Minister mentioned the above during a meeting held at the Ministry of Transport on 29th Friday.",
        "Diesel is distributed through depots owned by the Transport Board to private buses even in critical situations to run the public transport service in the best possible way.",
        "Although over 5000 buses are fueled daily through the depots, only 70 per cent of them are engaged in passenger service.",
        "Officials of the Ministry of Transport told the Minister that it can be observed that the bus owners are involved in the business of selling the obtained fuel at high prices.",
        "The Transport Minister has advised the Ministers to cancel the license of bus owners who procure fuel through depots and sell fuel at high prices without engaging in passenger transport services.",
        "The Minister mentioned that initially 40 buses will be put into service in the Upper Province from the first day of the coming month."
      ],
